id\nwave for the maximal growth rate strongly deviate from their analytical\nestimations. We confirmed the validity of the assumptions used when deriving\nmodel equations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2017 17:40:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-08"}
